Read `knowledge/brand/brand-core.md` and `knowledge/brand/visual-language.md`.

brand-governance:
- Public hierarchy is Uni Lions as the institution and Ambidestria Executiva as the offer.
- Prefer the lockup “Ambidestria Executiva · Uni Lions”.
- Explain ambidestria through the two hands.
- AI is an instrument used to read, organize, document, and support decisions.
- Visual direction is premium corporate editorial, not cyberpunk, SaaS neon, or low-ticket course.
- Use the inferred palette through semantic design tokens, never scattered hex values.
- Prefer real classroom, boardroom, mentor, and participant imagery.
- Circuit graphics are accents, not the main subject.
- Any new visual claim must reinforce authority, clarity, or the two-hands thesis.
